Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I go to Page 08 of Thoracic MRI
Then 'MRI follow-up' checkbox is enabled
And 'Biopsy recommended' checkbox is enabled
And 'Evaluation of interdisciplinary board' checkbox is enabled
And 'Further diagnostics' checkbox is enabled

And 'New' radio button is enabled
And 'Deterioration' radio button is enabled
And 'No change' radio button is enabled
And 'Improvement' radio button is enabled

And 'Bronchial carcinoma' radio button is enabled
And 'Pleural mesothelioma' radio button is enabled

When I select 'MRI follow-up' checkbox
Then '3 months' radio button is enabled
And '3-6 months' radio button is enabled
And '6-12 months' radio button is enabled
And '12 months' radio button is enabled
And '18-24 months' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Biopsy recommended' checkbox
Then 'Bronchoscopic' radio button is enabled
And '3-6 months' radio button is enabled
And 'US-guided' radio button is enabled
And 'Surgical' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Evaluation of interdisciplinary board' checkbox
Then 'Tumor board' checkbox is enabled
And 'Interstitial lung disease' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Further diagnostics' checkbox
Then 'CT thorax' checkbox is enabled
And 'CT abdomen' checkbox is enabled
And 'CT neck' checkbox is enabled
And 'Further diagnostics' checkbox is enabled
And 'MRI abdomen' checkbox is enabled
And 'MRI spine' checkbox is enabled
And 'MRI neck' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cardial diagnostics' checkbox is enabled
And 'CT Angiography' checkbox is enabled
And 'CTPA' checkbox is enabled
And 'PET-CT' checkbox is enabled
And 'SPECT' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bone scan' checkbox is enabled
